<emphasis id="A5C5C0B955ACC6D87601C3954C02D099" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="22">Delphinium staphisagria</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
L., Sp. Pl.: 531. 1753. TYPE: 
<emphasis id="81661BE65FCFDEDAA96C26C10879C1DD" italics="true" pageId="1" pageNumber="22">LINN 694/12</emphasis>
, Habitat in Istria, Dalmatia, Calabria, Apulia, Creta, Galloprovincia [South France]. The geographic origin of 
<normalizedToken id="9732DAF5B7A49ACBF9B9226ED4C8D12D" originalValue="Linneaus’s">Linneaus's</normalizedToken>
